          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Pre-apprenticeship Promotion Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires an application for a grant for demonstration projects to address health professions workforce needs to include a certification by the applicant that the development of the project included consideration of certain apprenticeship and pre-apprenticeship models.</p>]]>
        </text>
